#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.33:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.33:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga"
msgstr "4. Deities"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Hirigāravasutta"
msgstr "33. Respect for Conscience"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.33:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, "
"bhikkhave, sā devatā maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, tonight, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, "
"came to me, bowed, stood to one side, and said to me:"

msgctxt "an7.33:1.2"
msgid "‘sattime, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, these seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee."

msgctxt "an7.33:1.3"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.33:1.4"
msgid ""
"Satthugāravatā, dhammagāravatā, saṅghagāravatā, sikkhāgāravatā, "
"samādhigāravatā, hirigāravatā, ottappagāravatā."
msgstr ""
"Respect for the Teacher, for the teaching, for the Saṅgha, for the training, "
"for immersion, for conscience, and for prudence."

msgctxt "an7.33:1.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhante, satta dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī’ti."
msgstr "These seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.’"

msgctxt "an7.33:1.6"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, sā devatā."
msgstr "That is what that deity said."

msgctxt "an7.33:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then he bowed and respectfully circled me, keeping me on his right side, "
"before vanishing right there.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.1"
msgid "Satthugaru dhammagaru,"
msgstr "“Respect for the Teacher and the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.2"
msgid "saṅghe ca tibbagāravo;"
msgstr "and keen respect for the Saṅgha;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.3"
msgid "Samādhigaru ātāpī,"
msgstr "respect for immersion, being energetic,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:2.4"
msgid "sikkhāya tibbagāravo."
msgstr "and keen respect for the training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.1"
msgid "Hiriottappasampanno,"
msgstr "One with both conscience and prudence,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.2"
msgid "sappatisso sagāravo;"
msgstr "reverential and respectful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.3"
msgid "Abhabbo parihānāya,"
msgstr "can’t decline,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.33:3.4"
msgid "nibbānasseva santike”ti."
msgstr "and has drawn near to extinguishment.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.33:3.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
